      <title>Unicredit表示要计划与40亿欧元的德国贷款有关的SRT</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-18/unicredit-said-to-plan-srt-tied-to-4-billion-of-german-loans</link>
